vim has 4 modes

1. normal mode
2. insert mode
3. visual mode
4. command mode (:)



normal mode to insert mode

i: insert before cursor
I: insert before start of line
a: insert after cursor
A: insert after end of line
o: insert in next line
O: insert in previous line



insert mode to normal mode

press "esc"



normal mode to visual mode

press "v"



visual mode to normal mode
1. press "esc"
2. press "v"


normal mode to command mode

press ":"


command mode to normal mode

press "esc"
